      </p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
        <a href="/login" class="block w-full bg-red-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-xl hover:bg-red-700 transition-all transform hover:scale-[1.02] shadow-md">
